00:12:54.733 --> 00:12:56.026
Elle est partie.

00:13:01.782 --> 00:13:03.163
Le test habituel ?

00:13:03.283 --> 00:13:04.409
Absolument, Kylie.

00:13:04.743 --> 00:13:07.668
Un Terrien sera choisi au hasard,

00:13:07.788 --> 00:13:10.791
