00:13:50.330 --> 00:13:52.207
en cours...

00:13:55.252 --> 00:13:56.925
Terrien...

00:13:57.045 --> 00:13:58.761
Excellent choix !

00:13:58.881 --> 00:13:59.881
Attendez.

00:14:00.174 --> 00:14:01.675
