00:15:28.846 --> 00:15:31.103
Il a essayé de me remonter le moral.

00:15:31.223 --> 00:15:32.307
Il est homo ?

00:15:33.100 --> 00:15:34.100
Pardon ?

00:15:34.726 --> 00:15:38.277
Il est compatissant,
